## üî¨ Examples & Utilities

- `readme_test.py` ‚Äî basic client usage
- `stress_test.py` ‚Äî performance benchmarking, concurrency tests
- `connection_pooling.py` ‚Äî pooled connections for sync/async
- `flexible_config.py` ‚Äî shows all configuration options
- `rpc_coverage.py` ‚Äî full method coverage checker
- `zmq_notifications.py` ‚Äî live decoded transaction/block stream

Run with:
```bash
python3 -m evrmore_rpc.stress_test --sync --remote
```

---

## üß™ Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- Evrmore daemon running with RPC and optional ZMQ endpoints

